Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,嬢ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫　大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,落ち着いてじっとしてたら　すぐ治まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうして私が苦しくなったの　分かったの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,先家にいたら　窓の外で嬢ちゃんの声がしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,助けて　助けて　って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その方角にずっと行ったら　嬢ちゃんがいたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんと？すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:35.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私　ずっと「スミ助けて」って思ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　また苦しくなったら呼んでよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:40.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　スミ　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとうちにいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこにも遠くに行かないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さきほど　水路からチラリとお嬢さんをお見かけしたんですがね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:18.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お嬢さん　少々厄介な癖がお有りじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,癖？何のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,時折　抜け殻のようになって　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しばらく意識が戻らない　というような
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,放っておくと　ますます厄介なことになりますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,…ら　ゆら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やっと戻ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何の用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この人がその癖を治してくれるそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師のギンコと言います
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰も治してなんて言ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:34.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,出ていってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミと話してたもん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,またそれか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,バカなことを言ってないで　いい加減スミのことは忘れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:46.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれはもううちの使用人をやめたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でもスミは今でも　私が臥せってると分かってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「大丈夫」って言ってくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:00.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうしたら　苦しいのも楽になるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その人との間に　深い水脈が通ったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:12.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水脈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:19.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人と人の意識の間には　見えない通路があるという
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょうど　この町に張り巡らされた水路のように
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,裏庭ですべての水路は繋がっていて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:37.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこには「五識」を補うもの　我々の言う「妖質」というものが流れている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが水嵩が少ない所も多く　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おまけに入り組んでいて　地図もない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それでも水路は繋がっているので　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,望む相手に会えることもたまにある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すると　お互い同時に相手のことを思い出すようなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いわゆる「虫の知らせ」が起こるわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それを思うままに起こせる蟲がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,カイロギと言いましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妖質の豊かなものの意識に棲み
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:28.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,主と同調し　自由に水脈を往来し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,望む相手に思いを届けることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんのようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私がスミのこと離れてても分かるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも私のこと考えてくれてるからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲なんて関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:55.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたが必要とすれば　誰の所にも行けるはずなんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　繰り返しカイロギを使うと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,カイロギはやがて人の意識を乗せたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分の意思で動き始める
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:10.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すると人はその間　意識を奪われるようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:15.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そしていつかは　二度と意識は戻らなくなってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな　バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:26.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　当分その能力を使うのをやめさえすれば　害はない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,無理よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,発作が起きたら　いつの間にかスミの所へ行ってしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,相当進行しちまっているようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妖質を一時的に枯らす薬がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,飲めばカイロギは動けなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　発作が起きてスミの声が聞けなきゃ怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなもん　気のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,胸の病は　じっとして気を落ち着かせていれば大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,急には難しいかも知れんが　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた一人の問題じゃねぇんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,って？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミさんの方からこっちへ来ることはあったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　すでに伝染してるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:27.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,同じ所へ繰り返し行けば　相手にもカイロギがわく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,彼女の所へ行ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,薬　飲んどいた方が身のためだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:52.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,では　私も嬢ちゃんと話すのやめた方がいいと？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,嬢ちゃんは薬を飲むと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　どうだかね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと無理ね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:12.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子　ひどく寂しがり屋で　臆病で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私にも薬をいただけませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:27.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これを機に　もう繋がりを絶ちたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミが薬を…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:38.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あと　これを預かってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:00.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつでも困ったら呼んでねって言ったじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当は　ずっと　迷惑だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　そうなの　スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だったら　謝るから　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:21.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,答えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの　何があったの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,答えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう薬を飲んでしまったの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆら　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何やってんだ　いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,分かったわ　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,薬　飲むから一人にして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミが泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:56.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの　何があったの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私も少しは役に立てるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと頼ってばかりで　ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:25.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミ　話がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:31.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里へ帰すと？私何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:37.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　お前は母親代わりに本当によくやってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だがゆらはお前が来てから弱くなる一方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:49.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前に懐く余り　他のものを拒むようになってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,外で遊ぶこともせず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前とは話さなくても心が通じるなどと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それを諭せばますます拒む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:09.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前がそばにおる限り　ゆらは変わらんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまないが　あの子のためなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:28.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうよ　これでいいのよ　これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:01.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だめ　もうスミに頼っちゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だめ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここ　どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,町にあったかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:14.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰も…いない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妙なものが泳いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだ　戻らなきゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻ってスミの所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,竿がない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,違う　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そっちへ行きたいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:58.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どの枝も届きそうで届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どんどん流されてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怖い　そっちは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰か　お願い助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何　どうしたの　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:59.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんか今　夢に女の子が出てきて　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,海に流れされそうになってて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,女の子が助けてって言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おーい　ゆら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,手分けした方がいい　俺は向こうの水路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆら…か？
