Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆら　大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よかった　気がついたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃんと薬飲むまで見てるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:52.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ようやく懲りたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう戻れないかと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何度もああして　皆に迷惑をかけられないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだ　スミ　薬飲んだんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうして分かったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:16.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,結局　薬全部は飲めなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり嬢ちゃんが心配で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だめね　わざわざあんな文まで書いたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そっか　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　やっぱり寂しくなるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:42.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,会いに行きゃいいだろう　水路は変わらず繋がってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:47.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分で漕ぐのは無理なうちは　誰かの船に乗っけてもらえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,苦しくなりゃ　町の誰かが助けてくれるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　父さん　私そうしていい？
