Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もちろんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:36.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミ　遊びに来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また合図を送ったでしょう
